#Basepack of plugins for gstreamer

media-libs/gst-plugins-base alsa introspection ivorbis nls ogg orc pango theora vorbis X

# alsa		Add support for Advanced Linux Sound Architecture
# introspect	Add support for GObject based introspection
# ivorbis	Enable integer based vorbis decoder
# nls		Add Native Language Support
# ogg		Add support for the ogg container format (commonly used by Vorbis, Theora + flac)
# orc		Use dev-lang/orc for jit optimization of array operations
# pango		Enable pango GStreamer plugin
# theora	Add support for Theora Video Compression Codec
# vorbis	Add support for OggVorbis audio codec
